    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 2+ Warlock, Pact of the Blade feature</p></blockquote><p>Your pact weapon alters how certain weapon properties work when wielded by you.</p><p><strong>Heavy Swing.</strong> While wielding a weapon with the Versatile property in one hand, you can roll the weapon's damage as if you were wielding it with two hands.</p><p><strong>Long Throw.</strong> Thrown attacks at long range do not impose Disadvantage on your attack rolls, and the weapon can reappear in your hand as part of the same attack.</p><p><strong>Auto-Loading.</strong> You ignore the Loading property of the weapon.</p><p><strong>Extra Special.</strong> You do not reduce the damage die of a weapon that has its damage die reduced as a result of the Special property.</p>",
